==Noun==
===Angle===
1.  The [[three-dimensional]] [[shape]] formed of [[triangular]] [[sides]] and a [[rectangular]] [[base]].<br>
2.  A literal or figurative structure resembling a pyramid in having a broad or populous base and a thin or sparse [[pinnacle]].

See also: [[pyramid scheme]], [[ponzi scheme]]

